1 0 0 1 50 742 Tm (The result is not just analytical imprecision. It is institutional distortion. Regulatory) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 728 Tm (attention can be misdirected. Audit burdens can attach to the wrong actor. Users can be told) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 714 Tm (that "the system is supervised" without being told by whom, through what interface, or over) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 700 Tm (which actual action surfaces.) Tj
