1 0 0 1 50 490 Tm (## 9. Implications) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 476 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 462 Tm (### 9.1 For policy) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 448 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 434 Tm (Policy that governs only model access or model release may miss where deployer-level) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 420 Tm (authority actually resides.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 406 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 392 Tm (### 9.2 For procurement) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 378 Tm () Tj
