1 0 0 1 50 280 Tm (authority-not only benchmark scores and model identity.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 266 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 252 Tm (### 9.4 For responsibility allocation) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 238 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 224 Tm (When failures occur, post hoc analysis should ask who controlled infrastructure, memory,) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 210 Tm (approvals, and trace access, not only which model generated outputs.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 196 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 182 Tm (### 9.5 For public accountability) Tj
